overview: The user initiated a request to significantly improve the aesthetics
  of their sleep questionnaire app, feeling its current design was too generic.
  The agent undertook a comprehensive review, starting with an analysis of the
  existing color palette, typography, layout, and form elements. It then
  developed and implemented a new sleep-themed design, introducing a calming
  color palette of deep indigos, purples, and teal accents. Key changes included
  a redesigned main form layout with subtle background blurs and a star pattern,
  an enhanced intro section featuring interactive cards, and polished UI
  components like checkboxes, radio buttons, sliders, and progress bars. All
  questionnaire sections, including the report, were updated to ensure visual
  consistency and a more professional, inviting feel, moving away from a
  template-driven look to a nuanced, trustworthy interface.
